@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@itemStateId = paste-item-state-id-here
@bubbleSettingId = paste-bubble-setting-id-here

### 위젯 버블 표시 데이터 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 위젯 설정 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 위젯 설정 저장 (upsert)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bubbles": [
    {
      "bubbleType": "TODO",
      "enabled": true,
      "x": 100,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 400,
      "minimized": false,
      "opacity": 1.00,
      "ghostMode": false,
      "alertEnabled": true
    },
    {
      "bubbleType": "CHAT",
      "enabled": false
    }
  ]
}

### 위젯 컨텍스트 조회 (선택된 프로젝트룸)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/context
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 위젯 컨텍스트 저장 (프로젝트룸 선택)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/context
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selectedRoomId": null
}

### 버블 항목 상태 변경
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/items/{{itemStateId}}/state
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": "CONFIRMED"
}

### Tauri 사용 집계 저장
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/usage-summaries
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "device-abc123",
  "rollupKey": "device-abc123_2026-06-30_{{bubbleSettingId}}",
  "summaryDate": "2026-06-30",
  "bubbleSettingId": "{{bubbleSettingId}}",
  "openCount": 5,
  "interactionCount": 12,
  "visibleSeconds": 3600,
  "syncedAt": "2026-06-30T10:00:00Z"
}

### 오늘 사용 집계 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/widget/usage-summaries/today
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
